{ This chapter includes several key middlegame themes that have occurred in multiple games in the Petroff. Understanding the strategic concepts outlined in this chapter will assist you in absorbing the material in the theory chapters and help you make better decisions in practical games.  The themes covered are  🔵 Sacrificing thed4 pawn
  🔵 Control of the e-file PartsI andII
  🔵 Queen Sortie PartsI,II andIII
  🔵 Bishop and Queen battery
  🔵 The power of theKnight on e5
  🔵 Thec4 + d5 advance  🔵 Typical Knight maneuvers such asNf3-d2 andNh2-g4
  🔵 Theg4 advance  🔵 Play on thekingside
  🔵 Play on thequeenside
  A few of these themes are elaborated upon in themodel games chapter. }
