15... Qd7 16. Ra2
{ is a thematic maneuver in the Petroff, preparing to take over the e-file with Ra2-e2. }
16... Rad8 17. Rb2
{ White first probes Black's queenside, trying to induce weaknesses. } 17...
Qc8 18. h3 b6 19. Rbe2
{ gave White full control of the e-file in the game 1-0 @@StartBracket@@41@@EndBracket@@ Anand,V @@StartBracket@@2774@@EndBracket@@-Polgar,J @@StartBracket@@2718@@EndBracket@@ Mainz 2003. Black cannot contest this file with ...Rfe8 as the c7 pawn will hang at the end of the line. }
