1... Na5 2. Bf3 Qd7 3. Ne4
{ The threat of crippling Black's structure with Nxf6 practically forces } 3...
Bxe4 { when } 4. Bxe4
{ gave the bishop pair and a big advantage in the game 1-0 @@StartBracket@@31@@EndBracket@@ Polgar,J @@StartBracket@@2709@@EndBracket@@-Botsari,A @@StartBracket@@2313@@EndBracket@@ Achaea 2012. }
