Re1 O-O 9. Nbd2 Nd6 10. Nf1 Bxd3 11. Qxd3 c6 12. Bf4 Na6 13. h4 Nc7 14. Ng5 g6
{ is Black's best response. You can now choose between two different continuations:   🅰️ The novel  15.Nh2  is the neural network engines' top choice at high depth and is mymain recommendation. This is more challenging than  15.Ne3  but also more demanding  (for both White and Black!)  . There are some beautiful tactics in this variation, including a stunningqueen sacrifice! Now that's at least worth checking out xD   🅱️  15.Ne3  was Wesley So's choice in the Opera Euro Rapid tournament and is analyzed as analternative recommendation. This option is easier to learn, less demanding theoretically but sets Black fewer problems. Nevertheless, Black still needs to be very precise to maintain the balance. }
