11... dxc4 { is 3 times as popular as the alternatives. } 12. Bxc4 Nc2
{ With his king still in the middle of the board, Black has no time for these shenanigans. White can readily ignore Black's threat and instead develop with }
13. Bg5 { The point is that } 13... Nxa1 { loses to } 14. Re1+
