11. Nc3 Nxd5 { Black has just captured the d5 pawn. How should White respond? }
12. Bxh7+ { Boom, luring Black's king to h7 in order to hit him with Ng5+. }
12... Kxh7 13. Ng5+ Bxg5
{ 13...Kg8  14.Qxh5+-  leaves White with an extra pawn and an attack to boot.   13...Kg6  is no better. White is winning after  14.Qd3  f5  15.Ne6+−  with Qg3+ coming next. }
14. Qxh5+ Kg8
{ 14...Bh6  15.Nxd5  also leaves White a clear pawn up with an ongoing attack. }
15. Bxg5 { nets White a pawn with an ongoing initiative. } *

